India Today Black Planner with Cell Case:
Get more organised with this Planner which is specially offered by the house of India Today. This durable planner has an attractive embossed pattern that lends it a classy look. Comprising separate pockets for business and credit cards along with a stick-on pad and pen holder this planner is a thing of high utility. Not only this but you also get a stylish mobile cover along with this planner. Buy this planner from India Today and keep a proper track of your day.
